<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<%- include('head.ejs') %>

<body class="sb-nav-fixed">
  <% if (user.type === 9) { %>
  <%- include('navBar-admin.ejs') %>
  <% } else { %>
  <%- include('navBar-agent.ejs') %>
  <% } %>
  <%- include('modals.ejs', {user: user}) %>
  <div id="layoutSidenav">
    <% if (user.type === 9) { %>
    <%- include('sideBar-admin.ejs') %>
    <% } else { %>
    <%- include('sideBar-agent.ejs') %>
    <% } %> <div id="layoutSidenav_content">
      <main>
        <div class="container-fluid px-4">
          <h2 class="my-4">유저 매출내역 (베팅-획득)</h2>
          <div class="incomeDescription">
            <div class="alert alert-secondary d-inline-block fw-bold py-2" role="alert">
              <div>최총 루징금(E): 카지노 베팅획득(A) + 슬롯 베팅획득(B) - 카지노 롤링금(C) - 슬롯 롤링금(D)</div>
            </div>
            <div class="alert alert-secondary d-inline-block fw-bold py-2 mx-lg-3 me-1 mb-2" role="alert">
              <div>총 정산금(F): 최종 루징금(E) * 루징요율(G) / 100</div>
            </div>            
          </div>
          <div class="card mb-4">
            <div class="card-body">
              <table id="incomeUserBetWin" class="cell-border hover" style="width: 100%">
                <thead>
                  <tr>
                    <th rowspan="2"></th>
                    <th rowspan="2">IDX</th>
                    <th rowspan="2">정산일자</th>
                    <th rowspan="2">타입</th>
                    <th rowspan="2">아이디</th>
                    <th rowspan="2">닉네임</th>
                    <th colspan="2" class="text-center d-none d-lg-table-cell">현재 보유</th>
                    <th colspan="5" class="text-center d-none d-lg-table-cell">요율(%)</th>
                    <th colspan="3" class="text-center d-none d-lg-table-cell" id="betWinCasinoHeader">카지노</th>
                    <th colspan="3" class="text-center d-none d-lg-table-cell" id="betWinSlotHeader">슬롯</th>
                    <th colspan="2" class="text-center d-none d-lg-table-cell">획득 롤링</th>
                    <th colspan="2" class="text-center d-none d-lg-table-cell">정산</th>
                    <th rowspan="2">플래티넘</th>
                    <th rowspan="2">골드</th>
                    <th rowspan="2">실버</th>
                    <th rowspan="2">브론즈</th>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <th class="bg-gray">보유금</th>
                    <th class="bg-gray">포인트</th>
                    <th>카</th>
                    <th>슬</th>
                    <th>루(G)</th>
                    <th></th>
                    <th></th>
                    <th class="bg-gray">베팅</th>
                    <th class="bg-gray">획득</th>
                    <th class="bg-gray">베팅 - 획득(A)</th>
                    <th>베팅</th>
                    <th>획득</th>
                    <th>베팅 - 획득(B)</th>
                    <th class="bg-gray">카지노(C)</th>
                    <th class="bg-gray">슬롯(D)</th>
                    <th>최종 루징금 (E)</th>
                    <th>최종 정산금 (F)</th>
                  </tr>
                </thead>
              </table>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </main>

    </div>
  </div>
  <%- include('foot.ejs') %>
  <script src="/public/js/income.js"></script>
  <script src="/public/js/plugin/jquery-simple-tree-table.js"></script>
</body>

</html>